name: John BAILEY, Petitioner v. Leon A. KING, Lynne Abraham, First Judicial District of Pennsylvania, Respondents

opinions.text:
ORDER
Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 23rd day of June, 2008, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED and the Petition for Writ of Habeas Corpus is DENIED.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
